msgid "My load is too high, how can I reduce it?"
msgstr "Моя нагрузка слишком высока, как я могу ее снизить?"

#: ../../faq.rst:320
msgid ""
"(The previous documentation explained how to use turbo jpeg libraries as "
"an optimization technique. These libraries have long been part of "
